dataset.description: This dataset extracts information from a CSV file, specifically the source configuration data. It includes a single column 'a' with string values. This data is useful for understanding the source configuration of the system and can be used for troubleshooting and debugging purposes.

A dataset containing various types of data, including numeric, boolean, string, date, timestamp, array, and struct types. The dataset is stored in the Parquet format. It is used in multiple pipelines for data processing and analysis purposes.
